3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper addresses the issue of secure information exchange and proposes a method to confuse eavesdroppers, which is related to cryptography and security. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes an algorithm for joint design of the ZF matrix and the AN covariance matrix, which involves system optimization and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): Although not the main focus, the paper mentions simulation results, which may involve multimedia processing and analysis.
